    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/6de9aaf5cfa8fba1d5ace47490e6c130.poster.avif?t=1751031312\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/6de9aaf5cfa8fba1d5ace47490e6c130.webm?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/6de9aaf5cfa8fba1d5ace47490e6c130.mp4?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Chained in the Backrooms 是一款 1-4 人合作恐怖游戏。游戏中设有包含界限空间设计的关卡，您可以解决谜题、完成任务，并与设计独特的生物战斗。您的选择将影响游戏的进展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏基于一个流行的Creepypasta。与其他同类游戏不同，我们在每个关卡中都设计了不同的迷你游戏和谜题。随着关卡的推进，您将面对更恐怖和紧张的氛围。为了前进，您必须探索每个关卡，理解任务和迷你游戏，并学习如何应对生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在整个游戏过程中，您和队友被锁链连接在一起。锁链限制了您的行动，必须一起移动。这可能会使迷你游戏或逃离生物变得困难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以与环境元素互动以生存。周围有可供拾取的物品，这些物品可以用来恢复耐力和健康。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/7f0d91b3cb119b2db3675c70314f9c54.poster.avif?t=1751031312\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/7f0d91b3cb119b2db3675c70314f9c54.webm?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/7f0d91b3cb119b2db3675c70314f9c54.mp4?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>每个关卡可能包含不同的环境设计、谜题和生物。关卡过渡会提示给玩家。如果玩家失败，他们会从检查点重新开始。关卡之间没有关联，任务相互独立。随着游戏的推进，难度会逐渐增加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/916624de1a59c9e457541938410440b4.poster.avif?t=1751031312\" width=602 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/916624de1a59c9e457541938410440b4.webm?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/916624de1a59c9e457541938410440b4.mp4?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/2609bd9dcba3f09a82dee1aa3a56e1d0.poster.avif?t=1751031312\" width=800 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/2609bd9dcba3f09a82dee1aa3a56e1d0.webm?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060170/extras/2609bd9dcba3f09a82dee1aa3a56e1d0.mp4?t=1751031312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Backrooms 实际上是一个梦境。每当你通过一个关卡，你就会穿过梦的一层。要永远逃离 Backrooms，你必须克服并完成所有关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
